                     <title type="uniform">Hálfdanar saga gamla</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="is">Islandsk</textLang>
                     <rubric>Sagan<ex>n</ex> af <lb/> Hálfdáne Gamla oc Sonum<ex>m</ex>
                        h<ex>an</ex>s.</rubric>
                     <incipit>I. Cap<ex>itúli</ex> Daudi Hródgeírs. <lb/> Hríngr hefr Konungr
                        heítit, s<ex>e</ex>m Hríngarýci í N<ex>or</ex>egi er
                        v<ex>it</ex>ként</incipit>
                     <explicit>Lýcor hér nú at segja frá <lb/> Hálfdáni Gamla oc Sonum Hans, oc
                           Sam<lb rend="hyphenated"/>týdis món<ex>n</ex>um<ex>m</ex>
                        þeírra</explicit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem n="2" class="fas">
                     <locus from="25v:1" to="35r:13">25v-35r</locus>
                     <title type="uniform">Hálfs saga og Hálfsrekka</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="is">Islandsk</textLang>
                     <rubric>Sagan<ex>n</ex> Af <lb/> Hlfi Kóngi oc
                        Hlfs=Reckum<ex>m</ex>;</rubric>
                     <incipit>Cap<ex>itúli</ex> I<hi rend="sup">ti</hi>
                        <lb/> lfrecr hét K<ex>onun</ex>gr er bió  lfreksstød<ex>um</ex>,
                           h<ex>an</ex>n rédi f<ex>yrir</ex>
                        <lb/> Hrdalandi</incipit>
                     <explicit>Iri <lb/> hét dóttr hans, oc er þadan<ex>n</ex> mikill ætt
                           komin<ex>n</ex>. Oc <lb/> lýcor hér Sgo af Hlfi Kóngi <lb/> oc
                           Reckum<ex>m</ex> han<ex>n</ex>s.</explicit>
                     <filiation>Bl. <locus from="30r" to="38v">30r-38v</locus> i <ref type="ms"
                           target="#IBR04-0009-is">ÍBR 9 4to</ref> er en afskrift af denne
                        saga.</filiation>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem n="3" class="fas">
                     <locus from="35r:14" to="36v:15">35r-36v</locus>
                     <title type="uniform">Tóka þáttr Tókasonar</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="is">Islandsk</textLang>
                     <rubric>Þttur Af <lb/> Tóka Tókasýni.</rubric>
                     <incipit>I þan<ex>n</ex> Týma er Ólafr K<ex>onun</ex>gr hin<ex>n</ex> Helgi
                        rédi Noreg, bar þat til <lb/> eitt sin<ex>n</ex>i, er k<ex>onun</ex>gr sat í
                        Sarpsborg,</incipit>
                     <explicit>oc andadist í <lb/> Hvíta vodum<ex>m</ex>. <lb/> Oc lýcor þar Tóka
                        Þætti.</explicit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem n="4" class="fas">
                     <locus from="37r:1" to="78r:3">37r-78r</locus>
                     <title type="uniform">Starkaðar saga gamla</title>
                     <title type="parallel">Starkaðar saga Stórvirkssonar</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="is">Islandsk</textLang>
                     <rubric>Hér Byriar Saugo <lb/> af <lb/> Starkade enum<ex>m</ex> Gamla; <lb/>
                        Vikars Þáttur</rubric>
                     <incipit>Cap<ex>itúli</ex> I<hi rend="sup">ti</hi> f<ex>rá</ex> Stórkvirki
                        Starkadarsyni. <lb/> Húnþiófr hefr K<ex>onun</ex>gr heítit er rédi
                           f<ex>yrir</ex> Hørdal<ex>an</ex>di</incipit>
                     <explicit>oc sést h<ex>an</ex>s <lb/> Merki en<ex>n</ex> í Dag. Oc lýcor þar
                        Saugu <lb/> Starkadar ens Gamla.</explicit>
                     <note>Kapitel 20 på bl. <locus>60v</locus> begynder med rubrikken: <q
                           xml:lang="is">þáttur af <lb/> Helga Hvassa Hræreki K<ex>onun</ex>gi <lb/>
                           Haralde Hillditn<ex>n</ex>
                           <lb/> og <lb/> Brávallar Bardaga;</q> alle kapitler er forsynet med
                        titler.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem n="5">
                     <locus from="78r:4" to="78v:22">78r-v</locus>
                     <title type="supplied">Efterskrift</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="is">Islandsk</textLang>
                     <rubric>Til Lesarans.</rubric>
                     <incipit>Eg hefi vid þessa Søgu flýtirs Uppskrift, haft fyrir mér <lb/> tvö
                        Manúscripta en<ex>n</ex> þó hvörigt gott.</incipit>
